        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Upload your favorite photo, choose from unique shapes, and create personalized golf ball markers that make every round memorable.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
